title: Control panel for exercise equipment

claims.preamble: I claim the ornamental design for a control panel for exercise equipment, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front perspective view of a control panel for exercise equipment;
FIG. 2 is a front view of the control panel of FIG. 1;
FIG. 3 is a side view of the control panel of FIG. 1; and,
FIG. 4 is a top view of the control panel of FIG. 1.

The ornamental design that is claimed is shown in solid lines in the drawings. The broken (dashed) lines shown in the drawings are included for the purpose of illustrating environmental elements only and form no part of the claimed design.
